, \"to\": 1019}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1034}, {\"ngram\": \"Summer Games\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will do the same.\\\"\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1094, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC said it had received a number of assurances regarding the outstanding guarantees that include the state's Olympic delivery guarantee and the financial guarantees of the two regions involved - the Auvergne-Rhone-Alpes and Provence-Alpes-Cote d'Azur regions.\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1100, \"end\": 1103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.314953644261136e-24, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1300, \"end\": 1320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auvergne-Rh\\u00f4ne-Alpes\", \"score\": 0.9994302052301869, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Auvergne-Rhone-Alpes\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auvergne-Rh\\u00f4ne-Alpes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auvergne-Rh\\u00f4ne-Alpes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1133}, {\"ngram\": \"assurances\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1147}, {\"ngram\": \"the outstanding guarantees\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"the state's Olympic delivery guarantee\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"the financial guarantees\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"the two regions\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"Provence-Alpes-Cote d'Azur regions\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it said it would not countersign the host city contract, which has already been signed by France, until those guarantees were delivered.\", 