 1665, \"to\": 1671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The project aims to unite the north and south French Alps.\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1732, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The project\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"the north and south French Alps\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is a feeling of happiness,\\\" said French Olympic chief David Lappartient.\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1773, \"end\": 1779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999973007397834, \"rank\": 2.6952085772394724e-06, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1794, \"end\": 1811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lappartient\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Lappartient\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lappartient\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lappartient\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a feeling\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1752}, {\"ngram\": \"happiness\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"During the last year we spent massive on the bid.\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1863, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last year\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1834}, {\"ngram\": \"the bid\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now this is it.\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1879, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Never had an Olympic bid been so fast and then succeeded.\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1937, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic bid\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This allows us to follow the wave of Paris 2024, to benefit from their expertise,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 2032, \"entities\": [{\"